data.description: Welcome home to this very spacious 3 bedroom 1.5 bath in the desirable Palm Aire. This beautiful home offers a washer and dryer, freshly painted from ceiling to floor and new carpet throughout the second floor. New A/C, hurricane impact windows, 2 assigned parking spaces, and guest parking just steps from your door. This home also features French doors leading to a Key West Style patio. It is centrally located just minutes from spectacular beaches, major highways, the Fort Lauderdale Executive Airport and the DRV PNK Soccer Stadium! Pets allowed. This is the perfect home for you and your family!
